---
import ArrowIcon from './ArrowIcon.astro';
---

<div class="audience-grid">
  <article>
    <p class="section-number">01 · Dealer control path</p>
    <h3>Stress-test the operating system.</h3>
    <p>Assign an owner to the fact set, pay classification, calculation, legal route, matched record packet, and correction decision.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/tools/pay-system-analyzer/">Analyze one pay system <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
      <li><a href="/tools/wage-scenario-lab/">Decompose entered wage layers <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
      <li><a href="/dealers/">Open the dealer control path <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article>
    <p class="section-number">02 · Worker record path</p>
    <h3>Reconstruct one matched period.</h3>
    <p>Separate what happened, what each record shows, what contradicts it, and which question remains unresolved.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/pay-plans/">Open the closest role map <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
      <li><a href="/records/">Build the evidence packet <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
      <li><a href="/workers/">Open the worker reconstruction path <ArrowIcon /></a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</div>

<style>
  .audience-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; border-top: 4px solid var(--color-ink); border-bottom: var(--rule); }
  article { min-height: 26rem; padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); }
  article + article { border-left: 2px solid var(--color-ink); background: white; }
  h3 { max-width: 29rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); }
  article > p:not(.section-number) { max-width: 31rem; }
  ul { margin: 3rem 0 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  li { border-top: var(--rule); }
  li:last-child { border-bottom: var(--rule); }
  a { display: flex; min-height: 3.4rem; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { color: var(--color-cobalt-dark); }
  @media (max-width: 46rem) { .audience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } article { min-height: auto; } article + article { border-top: 2px solid var(--color-ink); border-left: 0; } }
</style>
